snippet.title: Mario a Plumber in time Re-Mastered reveal.
snippet.description:
(Music made by Tater Tot Tunes, please go subscribe to him too!)
( https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=16AcdBZM8-k&t=64s )

Well, I may be a little late then I expected, but It's out now! so please, play it!
https://drive.google.com/file/d/1zLhAE1s1Y1Cnxrgq-sCMSXvEKi4rSlhH/view?usp=sharing / https://www.dropbox.com/s/sqej2i64jlce5vb/Mario%20a%20Plumber%20in%20time%20Re-Mastered%20-%20Public%20Demo%20files.zip?dl=0

Oh! and also, PLEASE PLEASE PLEASE report bugs in the comment section of this video, or if you do a playthrough, on your own video!

It helps me improve the hacks quality tenfold.
And of course, you may be credited if you wish too~

One last thing, as this is a demo, the last level is 4-4, everything beyond that is either form the older version or just broken.

I'm not sure if there's much else I need to say, so I'll end it here.
Thank you very much for watching, please do subscribe if this caught your interest and share with others! it'll help me out a lot!

Until then, see you next time!
